Class ModificationFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.text.DocumentFilter
      • gui.ModificationFilter

  • public final class ModificationFilter
extends DocumentFilter
    This class filters input in TextArea. First it transmits a command to the engine (modify the Buffer). Then it apply this modifications to the GUI via Observer pattern
